<BYLINE>
<P>
By JIM COLONNA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ristorante Genovese, 214 N. Tustin Ave., Orange. Open Tuesday through Friday 
for lunch, 11 a.m. to 2 p.m.; Tuesday through Saturday for dinner, 5 to 10 p.m. 
(714) 633-5654. 
</P>
<P>
A family-run restaurant that's intimate yet casual, classy yet reasonable, and 
serves deep red, rich, garlic-laden sauce straight from the soul of Sicily. 
Pasta dishes are popular, and the steak a la Sicilian is extraordinary. But no 
place is perfect. It's closed Sunday and Monday.JIM COLONNA 
</P>
</TEXT>
