<TEXT>
<P>
Prego, 18420 Von Karman Ave., Irvine. Open Sundays till 10 p.m., Mondays till 
10:30, Tuesdays through Thursdays till 11, and Fridays and Saturdays till 
midnight. (714) 553-1333. Frazzled after a day on the fast track? Try a glass 
of Chianti Classico or a Sambuca Romana at Prego: It may be the best 
yuppie/muppie (for middle-aged) bar around here. On warm summer nights you can 
sit outside on the patio, where there's jazz on Thursdays and Fridays and 
chamber music on Saturdays, starting at 6:30 p.m. CLAUDIA LUTHER 
</P>
</TEXT>
