than seven years for killing three Arabs and maiming two Palestinian mayors. 
Dozens of West Bank settlers danced outside Maasiyahu Prison in the central 
Israeli town of Ramle as the three former members of the underground were 
released. Above, members of the crowd hoisted the three men -- Uzi Sharbav, 
left, Shaul Nir, center, and Menachem Livni -- on their shoulders. Associated 
Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
