BANKS -- PANAMA; BANK ACCOUNTS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN AID -- PANAMA; BANKING 
INDUSTRY -- PANAMA; PANAMA -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS; HINTON, DEANE R; UNITED 
STATES -- AMBASSADORS; PANAMA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
