<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOW MUCH HOSPITALS CHARGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What does it cost to stay in the hospital? It's a question that might depend on 
what insurance a patient does or doesn't have. Here is a sampling of daily room 
rates, without the benefit of insurance: 
</P>
