fires that broke out in three stores in Studio City. Two buildings were 
destroyed and damage was estimated at $2.5 million. Hundreds of people 
evacuated shops in the 12100 block of Ventura Boulevard as smoke billowed from 
the fire, above. MIKE MEADOWS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
