<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Terrell Lowery has been a bright spot for Loyola Marymount, which has 
struggled to a 2-7 start. BRIAN VANDER BRUG / Los Angeles Times; Table, 
LOWERY'S SEASON 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Profile 
</P>
