figures with 19. 
</P>
<P>
Antelope Valley 58, St. Francis 52 -- Kyle Barrett led St. Francis with a 
game-high 19 points and Willie Montgomery led Antelope Valley with 15. 
</P>
<P>
East Bakersfield 42, Palmdale 37 -- Palmdale limited its foe to two points in 
the third quarter but was outscored, 18-9, in the fourth. 
</P>
