Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122790-0139 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 327883 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 27, 1990, Thursday, Ventura County Edition 
