<HEADLINE>
<P>
DOWNEY Y SEEKS BASKETBALL COACHES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
DOWNEY 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Downey Family YMCA is accepting applications for volunteers to work as 
coaches and officials for its 1991 youth basketball season. 
</P>
<P>
The season will run from Jan. 5 to March 16. 
</P>
<P>
Training is available and experience is not necessary, but preferred. 
Applicants should enjoy working with children ages 5 to 12. Teams practice one 
night per week and games are on Saturdays. 
</P>
<P>
For more information or to apply, contact the Downey Family YMCA at 11531 
Downey Ave., or call 862-4201. 
</P>
