<TEXT>
<P>
California Bankshares Raises $4 Million in Capital: California Commercial 
Bankshares, the Santa Ana holding company of National Bank of Southern 
California, said that a rights offering to shareholders for 309,861 shares of 
common stock is fully subscribed. 
</P>
