under an arch at the company's center in Costa Mesa, which was built last year. 
AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, About 200 guests 
clinked glasses last week at Robert Mondavi Wine and Food Center. Mondavi wants 
to spread message that wine with a meal is OK. ; Photo, Visitors to the Robert 
